    "causal_summary": "Packet 046 deep research iteration-001 identified four concurrency defects in the skill-advisor daemon and freshness layer. Three are P1 (watcher flush reentrancy, lifecycle/shutdown ordering, generation lock-token theft) and one is P2 (out-of-order cache invalidation). Each defect lets the daemon's persisted state diverge from reality under realistic timer + shutdown + GC-pause interleavings.",
